description:
Bible Sequence is a simple program that teaches you the correct order of the books of the Bible.

When you start the game tiles will arrange themselves in random order. To win click on each tile in the order that they appear in the Bible. 

If you get stuck you can click &quot;Hint&quot; which will reveal the next Book. You get 2 chances to click on the next book's tile before you must start over. 

There's also an option to &quot;Solve&quot; which puts all the tiles in the correct order and ends the current game.

************************************************************************************

Players: One
Language: English
Operating System (Tested On): Windows 98, ME, XP

